{
  "id": "RAW_2a1adf",
  "title": "如何在 AI 时代取胜：每周发布一个功能，拥抱技术债务",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNjkzNDMzMA==&mid=2247483673&idx=1&sn=e2318638094166bc9cd7954b8e1eeb1d&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-04-07 03:51:00",
  "author": "yikai",
  "siteName": "yikai 的摸鱼笔记",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:16px 0;box-shadow:0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);max-width:100%;color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.2px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'PingFang SC', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">播客介绍与嘉宾背景</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">yikai</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">欢迎来到跨国串门计划，本期节目我们邀请到</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，他是Snap的早期核心成员，曾领导设计研发团队，并在微软等公司担任工程师。他现在是AI视频工具</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Captions</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的联合创始人兼CEO，该公司用户已超千万，融资超1亿美元。本期节目将深入探讨Gaurav在Snap和Captions的经验，包括独特的工程目标、</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">“黑科技路线”</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的秘密开发策略、AI视频技术的未来趋势与挑战，以及Snap设计师主导项目开发的运作模式。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\"></section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在这个时期真的很难得。五六年前创业特别困难，感觉所有领域都被人占据了。但现阶段很特别，做什么都能成功，我从业以来从没见过这么好的时机。能做的事比能做的人还多，这情况真是百年一遇。这种红利期总归会过去的，能参与其中真的很幸运。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在每天都有这么多变化，你们是怎么保持专注的？技术发展让工具开发变得容易，但如何让用户持续关注并使用产品变得更难，因为新奇的东西层出不穷。你在吸引和留住用户方面有什么经验？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在市场有很多宣传造势，你可以说“我们靠AI把这个产品彻底改造了”，很多人会好奇尝试。但关键是要兑现承诺，否则用户会流失。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">做产品最关键的还是解决真实痛点。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">很多人看到炫酷的功能就上头，但如果只是体验一下就走，构不成商业模式。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键不是为AI而AI，而是用AI解决实际痛点。商业逻辑没变：找准用户需求，用技术解决，找到需要方案的人群。技术变革带来了新产品形态，能解决以前解决不了的问题，这就是机会所在。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在每天都有爆炸性新闻，甚至</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AGI</span></span><span leaf=\"\">（通用人工智能）的突破似乎都不再遥远，但人们的反应却相对平静。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">这很魔幻。科幻小说里的场景（如《钢铁侠》里的贾维斯）正在实现，但大家反应却出奇平静。技术普及速度快得难以置信。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Captions独特的开发策略与产品哲学</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">你们如何持续吸引用户注意力并保持新鲜感？在信息洪流中如何保持清醒和专注？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在选择太多，优先级排序至关重要，要学会主动取舍。我们通过观察用户真实需求，特别是那些容易在社交媒体走红的内容来判断。这些内容通常触及用户痛点，即使是小痛点，抓住并结合业务调整，就能验证市场需求。我们团队深度使用社交媒体，实时追踪热点，了解用户喜好。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">小步迭代</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">我们的工程目标是：每个工程师每周都要交付一个可用的产品。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">所谓“可用”，是指用户会专门冲着这个新功能来使用你的应用，是别人没有的独门绝活。我们采用极致精简开发策略，把设计方案减到最核心的功能模块（MVP），上线后收集真实用户痛点，明确后续迭代方向。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">每个工程师每周交付一个可用产品，这个目标很有挑战性。如何保证质量和产品一致性？对想尝试这种模式的团队有什么建议？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">质量需要取舍，但底线是功能必须能正常运行。压缩时间的关键不是砍质量，而是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">精简需求</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。反复问自己：这个功能砍掉会怎样？产品还能用吗？一直砍到不能再砍为止，就能抓住最核心的问题。先做最基础的MVP，用户使用后会暴露最难受的点，我们就能快速响应解决。用户抱怨反而是好事，说明他们在乎。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于需要数周的长期项目，如基础设施和后端工作，我们通常在第四季度集中处理</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术债</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">创业公司应该主动承担技术债——这是我们能比大公司行动更快的关键。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">大公司要么当场解决，要么在为早期遗留问题买单。我们把问题留给未来的工程师解决，这就像贷款，是为了用小资源撬动大项目。当然，技术债有利息（日常维护时间），积累过多会拖垮开发新功能的能力，需要把握平衡。对于不可逆的关键决策，我们会花更多时间评估。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI编程工具（如</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Devin</span></span><span leaf=\"\">）对你们团队效率提升有多大？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">绝对是百分百的提升。现在大家都在用，是效率神器。小公司能快速采用这些新工具，这是我们的优势。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">你们在研发流程或团队搭建方面，有什么特别值得借鉴的做法吗？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们有两条产品路线。一条是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">公开版</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，主要基于用户反馈和公开需求，比如去背景、撤销重做、上传长视频等。这些功能竞品也清楚，很难形成核心壁垒。另一条是内部称为</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">“黑科技路线”</span></span><span leaf=\"\">（或“机密路线”）的保密开发计划。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">这些功能完全基于我们对行业的独到理解，用户可能从未提过，甚至一开始看不懂，但它们旨在彻底颠覆用户习惯，带来惊喜。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">这是工程、招聘等多部门集思广益的结果，通过内部投票筛选，产品团队评估可行性。真正能颠覆行业的东西往往藏在机密路线里。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如，我们早期的AI功能</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">“眼神接触”</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，能自动调整视频中人物眼神看向镜头。这是我们首创，与NVIDIA合作实现。这个功能解决了创作者看提词器导致眼神不自然的痛点，上线后反响热烈，演示视频在全球疯传，现在已被广泛借鉴。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">你们会用AI辅助头脑风暴构思这些核心创意吗？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前还没做到，主要卡在语境理解。要让AI理解抽象的用户和用例很难，我自己都很难清晰描述这种直觉。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Snap独特的组织文化与产品方法</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">Snap CEO</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Evan Spiegel</span></span><span leaf=\"\">对用户的洞察力无人能比。他经常提出大家不看好的点子，但做出来总能成功。例如，坚持称Snap为</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">相机公司</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，并将打开App即是相机作为核心设计，这使其在关键时刻（如抓拍朋友搞怪瞬间）比需要加载界面的应用更快，成为制胜关键。我也是后来才领悟到这点。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">Snapchat是最后一个真正火起来的新社交平台（除TikTok外）。外界对其运作模式了解不多。你认为Snap成功的关键因素是什么？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">Snap做得最到位的是坚持创新，以应对激烈的竞争。他们建立了一套独特的运作模式：CEO是产品导向型人才，围绕一个精干的</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心设计团队</span></span><span leaf=\"\">（10-12人，即使公司几千人规模时也是如此）运转。很长一段时间没有产品经理（PM），尤其是在创新爆发期。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">这些设计师实际上是既做设计又当产品经理的设计师，负责产品路线、文档、协调、上线等所有环节，需要懂技术、用户体验、界面设计和商业逻辑。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">工作强度大，薪酬也高。这种模式让CEO能细致把控每个面向用户的功能改动。要加新界面，必须通过这少数几个能直接与CEO沟通的设计师，形成了严格的管控流程。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">有说法认为成功的消费级应用需要一个事无巨细的核心决策者，Evan通过与设计团队紧密配合实现了这一点。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">完全同意。他脑子里装着整个应用的细节，对产品路线有惊人的微观把控能力，并且能带动团队实现质的飞跃。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人羡慕Snap不设PM的模式，认为PM只会拖慢进度。为什么这些设计师能胜任？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些设计师都是专家级，且规定不能有下属，必须亲力亲为。他们工作特别拼，公司也给予了极高的回报。这种复合型人才非常难找。后来我在Snap创建了</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">“设计工程师”</span></span><span leaf=\"\">角色，结合设计和编程能力，能独立完成从构思到发布的全过程。这个小团队专门负责快速原型验证，将原型在小范围（如澳大利亚或几所高中）测试，获取真实数据，验证后再投入大规模工程资源。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">有趣的是，我们发现可以通过</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">内部病毒式传播</span></span><span leaf=\"\">来统一团队目标。将测试版安装包发到内部群，如果反响热烈，会迅速传遍公司，甚至引起高层关注，从而自下而上地推动项目立项。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在很多PM直接做原型，AI工具也使之更容易。你们现在为什么不直接做原型，而是选择快速发布？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们的发布流程已经很快（一周），直接上线收集用户反馈效果更好。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">Snap的架构很有趣，有设计工程师，设计产品经理。工程师本身也像产品导向的项目经理。你们现在Captions为什么选择分开设置PM、工程师和设计师的职能？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">我认为</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">角色很关键。Snap不设PM是特例。总得有人做这些工作。在Captions，我们要求PM不仅懂产品，还要懂市场推广，理解如何找到目标用户群。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">产品经理其实应该把市场推广的活儿也包圆了，因为这本质上也是产品设计的一部分，是从用户点击广告到完成引导的全流程。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">我们希望每个部门都深入了解其他部门，做出决策时能考虑全局。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">这和Airbnb创始人Brian Chesky将PM改为产品营销经理的理念相似。招PM时是否看重市场敏感度？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">是的，至少要有潜力。用户研究的价值不在于直接告诉你做什么，而是帮助产品负责人建立对用户需求和痛点的深刻理解模型。Snap虽然用户研究部门很小，但高层对用户行为有深刻洞察，并坚守核心价值观（如安全私密分享），以此划定产品边界，拒绝不符理念的功能，即使它们可能很火（如公开转发、算法推荐内容）。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI视频的未来：真实性、伦理与应用</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们离AI生成内容真假难辨的时代还有多远？这对世界有何影响？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">影响是根本性的。视频、图像、音频不可信已有一段时间。如果一切都能逼真伪造，我们可能回到</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">“口说无凭”</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的时代，只能依赖物证和口供。这很令人担忧，但也催生了解决验证难题的商机。以假乱真的视频技术已接近实现，可能还需要两三年达到完美。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI生成视频大致分两类：一是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">记录生活</span></span><span leaf=\"\">或</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">纪实类</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，如生活片段、新闻现场。伪造这类内容完全是负面的，必须在产品设计中杜绝。另一类是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">讲故事</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的内容，如广告、社交媒体、影视剧，目的是娱乐或传递信息。这类内容大家都知道是虚构的（如会说话的动物广告），如果AI能帮助更多人讲故事，是积极的。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">我们的产品设计思路是：把不好的使用方式彻底堵死，让正向使用变得特别简单。</span>\n     </section>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前文生视频主要是无声画面或素材，但大部分内容（影视剧、社交媒体）核心是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">对话和独白</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。我们专注于解决对话视频的制作问题，目前这个方向研究不多，技术仍有挑战。字节跳动发布的模型是大型扩散模型生成对话视频的典型案例，效果惊人，技术路线与主流数字人公司不同。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI视频技术发展速度惊人（对比一两年前威尔史密斯吃意面视频）。你认为营销领域会是AI视频最先落地的场景吗？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">是的。技术再酷，普及也需要时间。公司需要找到对的营销方式触达用户。我们用AI生成视频广告时，早期用户会觉得假，但技术成熟后，质疑声消失了。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">AI生成可以一次性产生大量版本，总有版本效果比真人录制更好。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">AI还能高效完成</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">本地化</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，翻译效果接近原版。这股浪潮会席卷市场，很快在社交媒体普及。未来可能出现完全由AI生成内容和虚拟用户的社交平台，算法为你量身定制一切，这可能五年内实现。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">经验教训与闪电问答</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">分享一下你的失败经历或遇到的挫折？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">公司刚起步时，我们花两天做了个</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">字幕应用</span></span><span leaf=\"\">并上线，结果意外爆火，冲到应用商店第一。但因为太顺利，我们反而分心去探索社交网络功能，忽视了已经展现出强大产品市场契合度的字幕系统。一年半后，我偶然发现这个几乎无人维护、bug未修、客服积压的应用，居然靠自然增长带来了50万美元收入，增长曲线一飞冲天。这信号太明显了！我们浪费了一年半时间，本应全力投入这个方向。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在做新社交平台还有可能成功吗？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">完全有可能。我们之前下架的那个社交App，至今仍有成千上万用户在使用，证明了社交网络的强大生命力。建立不易，摧毁也难，推特/X就是例子。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 500;background: rgba(255,246,214,0.4);box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,217,123,0.15);border-radius: 2px;padding: 0 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">闪电问答环节：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">最常推荐的书？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">我特意不培养阅读能力，把精力放在听和看上，觉得这才是未来方向。（书架上的书都没读过）</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近喜欢的电影或剧？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">《Silo》和《Severance》。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近让你上头的产品？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Linear</span></span><span leaf=\"\">（项目管理工具）和</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Superhuman</span></span><span leaf=\"\">（邮件客户端）。设计好用，每天都在用。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">你的人生格言或常说的话？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">我喜欢竞争和赢。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">想要赢，必须做到极致。成为最佳的最简单方法，就是抢占先机。</span>\n     </section>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近看过最惊艳的AI视频？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">OmniHuman</span></span><span leaf=\"\">项目（抖音上的会说话的西兰花视频），效果惊艳。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语与招募信息</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">听众在哪里可以找到你和你的项目？大家能为你做些什么？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以在LinkedIn上找到我，私信开放。我们正在搭建早期的</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">产品和设计团队</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，如果你对AI视频和消费级应用感兴趣，现在是加入Captions的好时机。我们是精干的初创团队，紧密配合，每周发布新功能。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">这对喜欢快节奏的产品经理是理想状态。Gaurav，非常感谢你今天的分享。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gaurav Misra</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">谢谢邀请，非常感谢。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Captions CEO 分享 AI 视频工具的开发策略、产品哲学和 Snap 的独特经验，强调快速迭代、解决痛点、拥抱技术债务，并探讨了 AI 视频的未来趋势。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Captions CEO 分享 AI 视频工具的开发策略、产品哲学和 Snap 的独特经验，强调快速迭代、解决痛点、拥抱技术债务，并探讨了 AI 视频的未来趋势。",
  "summary": "Gaurav Misra，AI 视频工具 Captions 的联合创始人兼 CEO，分享了他在 Snap 和 Captions 的经验。他强调在 AI 时代，关键是利用 AI 解决实际痛点，而非为 AI 而 AI。Captions 采取每周发布一个功能的快速迭代策略，允许承担技术债务以加速产品开发。同时，Gaurav 还分享了 Snap 独特的组织文化，包括设计师主导产品开发和 CEO 对产品细节的严格把控，这种模式使得 Snap 能够快速创新并应对激烈的市场竞争。此外，他还对 AI 视频的未来趋势和伦理问题进行了探讨，并介绍了 Captions 在 AI 视频领域的具体创新，例如眼神接触功能。最后，Gaurav 还分享了他的失败经历和对未来社交平台的看法。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 时代的关键是用 AI 解决实际痛点，而非为 AI 而 AI",
      "explanation": "技术变革带来了新产品形态，能解决以前解决不了的问题，商业逻辑没变，找准用户需求，用技术解决，找到需要方案的人群。"
    },
    {
      "point": "创业公司应主动承担技术债务，以小资源撬动大项目",
      "explanation": "将问题留给未来的工程师解决，这就像贷款，是为了用小资源撬动大项目，但需要把握平衡，避免技术债积累过多拖垮开发新功能的能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "快速迭代是验证市场需求的有效方式",
      "explanation": "通过观察用户真实需求，特别是那些容易在社交媒体走红的内容来判断。这些内容通常触及用户痛点，即使是小痛点，抓住并结合业务调整，就能验证市场需求。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Snap 的设计师主导模式是其成功的关键因素之一",
      "explanation": "Snap 建立了一套独特的运作模式：CEO 是产品导向型人才，围绕一个精干的核心设计团队运转。这种模式让 CEO 能细致把控每个面向用户的功能改动，形成了严格的管控流程。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "现在这个时期真的很难得。现阶段很特别，做什么都能成功，我从业以来从没见过这么好的时机。",
    "关键不是为 AI 而 AI，而是用 AI 解决实际痛点。",
    "创业公司应该主动承担技术债 ------ 这是我们能比大公司行动更快的关键。",
    "想要赢，必须做到极致。成为最佳的最简单方法，就是抢占先机。",
    "我们的产品设计思路是：把不好的使用方式彻底堵死，让正向使用变得特别简单。"
  ],
